ref=\"http://forgani.com/index.php/tools/wpclassiefied-plugins/\"><strong>wp-classified</strong></a></p>\n<p>The wpClassified plugin allows you to add a simple classifieds page in to your WordPress blog.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.crazyiven.de/wordpress-plugins/mytreasures/\"><strong>myTreasures</strong></a></p>\n<p>The myTreasures project derived from the idea of presenting your own dvd collection nice and informatively in the internet.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.commentluv.com/download/ajax-commentluv-installation/\"><strong>CommentLuv</strong></a></p>\n<p>Appends a titled link using AJAX to the authors last blog post on their comment giving back some luv to the people that join your discussion</p>\";}i:23;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:47:\"Gravatar: Gravatar Importer for Google Contacts\";s:4:\"guid\";s:35:\"http://gravatar.wordpress.com/?p=84\";s:4:\"link\";s:61:\"http://blog.gravatar.com/2008/10/13/gravatar-importer-google/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1570:\"<div class=\"snap_preview\"><br /><p><a href=\"http://www.arikfr.com/blog/about\">Arik Fraimovich</a> has released <a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/gravatar-importer/\">an open source .NET app</a> that <a href=\"http://www.arikfr.com/blog/gravats-to-google-contacts-importer.html\">syncs your Google contacts with their Gravatars</a>, using the <a href=\"http://code.google.com/apis/contacts/\">Google Contacts Data API</a>.</p>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/gravatar.wordpress.com/84/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/gravatar.wordpress.com/84/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/gravatar.wordpress.com/84/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/gravatar.wordpress.com/84/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/gravatar.wordpress.com/84/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wor