tes all permalinks. In addition, it also gives the user the option to update any links within posts and pages.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.frank-verhoeven.com/wordpress-plugin-fv-community-news/\"><strong>FV Community News</strong></a></p>\n<p>Allow your visitors to add articles to the sidebar or anywhere else. Complete with moderation panel and a settings page, you can sit back while you have full control about the look and articles that being posted.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.mydigitallife.info/2008/10/06/caption-disabler-wordpress-plugin-to-disable-and-remove-captions-functionality/\"><strong>Caption Disabler</strong></a></p>\n<p>Caption Disabler is a WordPress plugin that removes and disables captions feature in WordPress so that all caption shortcode is not been parsed or translated, and no  and  HTML entities are automatically added while editing or writing.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/jquery-reply-to-comment/\"><strong>jQuery Reply to Comment</strong></a></p>\n<p>Add &#8220;reply&#8221; and &#8220;quote&#8221; features on each comment list.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://urbangiraffe.com/plugins/redirection/\"><strong>Redirection</strong></a></p>\n<p>Redirection is a WordPress plugin to manage 301 redirections, keep track of 404 errors, and generally tidy up any loose ends your site may have.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.glockeasymail.com/wordpress-email-newsletter-plugin-for-double-opt-in-subscription/\"><strong>WP Double Opt-In List Management</strong></a></p>\n<p>This WordPress email list management plugin allows the visitors of your blog subscribe to your mailing list using a double opt-in method. The signup form (Email, Name and other fields) is placed on the WordPress blog sidebar. After a user fills in the form and clicks &#8220;Subscribe&#8221;, WP double opt-in plugin sends an email with the subscription confirmation link to the user.</p>\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Mon, 06 Oct 2008 14:11:30 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\